The queues stretched from the stadium right up to the intersection at Tosca Supermarket – testament to the huge demand for property in Middelburg.  Thousands of people queued around Kees Taljaard Stadium on Tuesday to apply for residential stands which the municipality has made available in Rockdale.  The municipality will allocate stands to applicants through means of a draw later this week. • See the full story in this Friday’s edition of the Middelburg Observer.